### Custom Styles (styles.css)

Create a file in your project directory called `styles.css`, and paste in this custom purple-themed style:

```css
body {
  background-color: #f8f4fc;
  color: #4b2e83;
  font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
}

.navbar, .quarto-title-banner {
  background-color: #7e57c2;
  color: white;
}

h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6 {
  color: #512da8;
}

a {
  color: #6a1b9a;
}

a:hover {
  color: #ab47bc;
}

